msgstr "We vermenigvuldigen [code]power[/code] met [code]level[/code] met behulp van [code]*[/code] en komen uit op [code]15[/code]."

#: course/lesson-14-multiplying/lesson.bbcode:63
msgid "We can use [code]*=[/code] in the same way as [code]-=[/code] and [code]+=[/code]."
msgstr "We kunnen [code]*=[/code] op dezelfde manier gebruiken als [code]-=[/code] en [code]+=[/code]."

#. TRANSLATORS: Quiz question
#: course/lesson-14-multiplying/lesson.bbcode:63
msgid "What is the value of damage now?"
msgstr "Wat is de waarde van damage nu?"

#. TRANSLATORS: Quiz content
